When to Use Each Prompt:

Prompt File	                When to Use	                    How to Use

00_session_starter.md       Every single session	        Paste first, wait for confirmation, Then give your task

01_fix_bugs.md	            Fixing BUG-001, 002, 003	    Paste after session starter, add "Fix BUG-001, BUG-002, BUG-003" at the bottom

02_add_strategy.md	        Adding S2 or any new strategy   Paste after session starter, describe the new strategy at the bottom

03_review_before_deploy.md	Before going live on Hetzner	Paste after session starter, attach the changed files at the bottom

